{"tid":1397033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】富衛: 近兩月事件影響未算大 周一可彈性上班","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:49:31.000Z","uid":55360,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"840efc820187b541f57782d44eb71cd59bb56123","tid":1397033,"uid":55360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】富衛: 近兩月事件影響未算大 周一可彈性上班<br />\n<br />\n近月本港社會運動持續，部份內地客因而延遲或取消來港投保。富衛香港及澳門首席營銷總監王君傑表示，會密切留意事態發展，雖然「唔多唔少會有影響」，但就最近兩個月而言，對富衛影響未算太大，保費增長亦見不錯。<br />\n<br />\n至於市民發起周一罷工，他表示旗下員工有彈性工作安排。<br />\n<br />\n香港寬頻（1310）今日亦發內部通告，稱下周反《逃犯條例》修定示威，有機會出現堵塞馬路情況，呼籲同事上班小心，如未能上班請盡早通知上司，並安排在家工作，亦建議本周末帶公司電腦回家，預備下周未能上班時在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190802&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59889243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190802%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59889243&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9f53c8f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190802%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59889243&h=f72418fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190802&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59889243</a>"},{"pid":"cf7b347e346ee6cbaeb4cf0057c71582ec6fd6bb","tid":1397033,"uid":55360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"9c9b24479b3ed40c47a02818e7fa80ebe2d534fe","tid":1397033,"uid":25440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"［代發］一群政府新聞主任的公開信<br />\n有職員證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今晚7點中環遮打花園見！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki